{"tid":2298682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《離思五首·其四》元稹","createTime":"2020-11-24T08:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T09:38:41.000Z","uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a57460883018d25ce808cbbe61a225030728fb","tid":2298682,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"曾經滄海難爲水，除卻巫山不是雲。<br />\n取次花叢懶回顧，半緣修道半緣君。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾經到臨過滄海，別處的水就不足爲顧；若除了巫山，別處的雲便不稱其爲雲。倉促地由花叢中走過，懶得回頭顧盼；這緣由，一半是因爲修道人的清心寡慾，一半是因爲曾經擁有過的你。"},{"pid":"441c7cc127d2475da72a4a06a9c6258424952a35","tid":2298682,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"春有百花秋有月，夏有涼風冬有雪。<br />\n若無閒事掛心頭，便是人間好時節。<br />\n<br />\n🍷"},{"pid":"14a715e035a7c6d29b637d3634974f124660e462","tid":2298682,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"回家回家回回家"},{"pid":"26757f81671b9004c55ce0b8191eb3115fb37d59","tid":2298682,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"回家當天的所愛是隻狗🐶🥃"},{"pid":"33c1a8250badf39dcc57c613a77ca79ccc657c33","tid":2298682,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回頭當天的所愛是隻狗🐶🥃</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3aa8a9c0f2e6ef523a71a56d53edd1ffc32720c","tid":2298682,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a715e035a7c6d29b637d3634974f124660e462","tid":2298682,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"回家回家回回家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"雨雨風風花花葉葉年年暮暮朝朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220656b0de009cd89212f2ce383a7d91cb618690","tid":2298682,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"441c7cc127d2475da72a4a06a9c6258424952a35","tid":2298682,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislik